headline: Erie Indemnity: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: ERIE, Pa. AP) — Erie Indemnity Co. (ERIE) on Thursday reported net income of $152 million in its fourth quarter. On a per-share basis, the Erie, Pennsylvania-based company said it had profit of $2.91.

headline: Erie Indemnity Reports Full Year and Fourth Quarter 2024 Results
summary: Erie Indemnity Company (NASDAQ: ERIE) today announced financial results for the full year and quarter ending December 31, 2024. Net income was $600.3 million, or $11.48 per diluted share, in 2024, compared to $446.1 million, or $8.53 per diluted share, in 2023. Net income was $152.0 million, or $2.91 per diluted share, in the fourth quarter of 2024, compared to $110.9 million, or $2.12 per diluted share, in the fourth quarter of 2023.
